00:19:47,394 --> 00:19:48,728
- You lead.
- Can I take it back?

503
00:19:48,729 --> 00:19:49,645
No, you can't.

504
00:19:49,646 --> 00:19:50,771
CHANGING HIS MIND NEXT SECOND

505
00:19:50,772 --> 00:19:52,815
- It helps to know the story.
- That's true.

506
00:19:52,816 --> 00:19:54,400
- I feel a bit less scared.
- Let's go.

507
00:19:54,401 --> 00:19:56,611
- Really?
- Doesn't knowing the story make it scary?

508
00:19:56,612 --> 00:19:59,448
I really think I'm going to cry.

509
00:20:00,324 --> 00:20:01,324
THE SCAREDY-CATS WALK OUT CRYING

510
00:20:01,325 --> 00:20:02,617
I think I will just freeze up.

511
00:20:02,618 --> 00:20:04,076
- I think I might punch the ghost.
- Yes.

512
00:20:04,077 --> 00:20:04,994
I will punch them.

513
00:20:04,995 --> 00:20:06,204
- I mean it.
- Me too.

514
00:20:06,205 --> 00:20:07,496
I will hit them.

515
00:20:07,497 --> 00:20:09,207
- I have a weapon.
- I will attack.

516
00:20:09,208 --> 00:20:10,791
- I'm armed.
- It's a back scratcher.

517
00:20:10,792 --> 00:20:12,710
- It can be deadly.
- Give me the blade.

518
00:20:12,711 --> 00:20:14,378
- The blade? Okay.
- Yeah.

519
00:20:14,379 --> 00:20:15,838
- I want the blade.
- There you go.

520
00:20:15,839 --> 00:20:17,465
Jin-su--

521
00:20:17,466 --> 00:20:18,716
- We need it.
- I will hit them.

522
00:20:18,717 --> 00:20:21,260
Jin-su needs to protect us.

523
00:20:21,261 --> 00:20:25,306
I think this could be useful
if Jin-su gets angry.

524
00:20:25,307 --> 00:20:28,352
- It could be used to appease him.
- Yes.

525
00:20:29,311 --> 00:20:30,561
It's okay.

526
00:20:30,562 --> 00:20:32,396
- Is it okay?
- How can we go there?

527
00:20:32,397 --> 00:20:33,814
It's okay.

528
00:20:33,815 --> 00:20:34,982
I'm going to hit them.

529
00:20:34,983 --> 00:20:36,193
I'm getting goosebumps.

530
00:20:36,735 --> 00:20:38,319
We need to find that road.

531
00:20:38,320 --> 00:20:40,404
- There it is. The Buddha statue.
- It's here.

532
00:20:40,405 --> 00:20:41,822
- It's right here.
- Yes.

533
00:20:41,823 --> 00:20:45,201
<i>Look at this.</i>

534
00:20:45,202 --> 00:20:48,830
THE STONE STATUE FROM AHN MU-SEONG'S VIDEO

535
00:20:49,748 --> 00:20:51,082
Let's go.

536
00:20:51,083 --> 00:20:52,792
Is this the right thing to do?

537
00:20:52,793 --> 00:20:53,751
Why do we need to?

538
00:20:53,752 --> 00:20:55,294
- There's no reason, right?
- Right?

539
00:20:55,295 --> 00:20:57,463
- What do we need to find in there?
- We have to go.

540
00:20:57,464 --> 00:20:58,673
- I have a feeling…
- Yes?

541
00:20:58,674 --> 00:21:00,967
…that the final boss
is waiting for us in there.

542
00:21:00,968 --> 00:21:03,302
Are we going to walk in without a plan?

543
00:21:03,303 --> 00:21:05,888
Don't we need to examine the camera

544
00:21:05,889 --> 00:21:07,181
- that Ahn Mu-seong dropped?
- Yes.

545
00:21:07,182 --> 00:21:09,976
- But there's a ghost in there.
- We need to find out what happened.

546
00:21:09,977 --> 00:21:12,561
We need to find the cause.

547
00:21:12,562 --> 00:21:14,063
Yes, but…

548
00:21:14,064 --> 00:21:15,523
INTENSE TUG OF WAR

549
00:21:15,524 --> 00:21:16,983
I know we have to, but I don't want to.

550
00:21:16,984 --> 00:21:18,901
I just think…

551
00:21:18,902 --> 00:21:22,238
It just seemed like a crazy thing to do.

552
00:21:22,239 --> 00:21:24,448
We were going to a place
where we knew there was a ghost.

553
00:21:24,449 --> 00:21:25,866
Okay, let's just go.

554
00:21:25,867 --> 00:21:27,493
Yes, that's where he did his catchphrase.

555
00:21:27,494 --> 00:21:29,829
- Ahn Mu-seong's Unsung Ghosts.
- Unsung Ghosts!

556
00:21:29,830 --> 00:21:31,038
Gabee's Unsung Ghosts.

557
00:21:31,039 --> 00:21:33,125
- I am terrified.
- Gabee is scared.

558
00:21:33,834 --> 00:21:34,835
It's okay.

559
00:21:35,419 --> 00:21:37,586
- We're really going?
- Yes?

560
00:21:37,587 --> 00:21:42,008
AT THE ENTRANCE ALREADY

561
00:21:42,009 --> 00:21:44,051
- We must be really careful.
- It's open.

562
00:21:44,052 --> 00:21:45,220
It's open?

563
00:21:45,721 --> 00:21:47,097
Oh, gosh.

564
00:21:54,104 --> 00:21:57,148
THE CHAINS THAT AHN MU-SEONG BROKE

565
00:21:57,149 --> 00:21:59,526
It's the same as in the video.
He used this cutter.

566
00:22:00,360 --> 00:22:03,529
THE DOOR IS SLIGHTLY OPEN

567
00:22:03,530 --> 00:22:05,072
Will we find Ahn Mu-seong?

568
00:22:05,073 --> 00:22:06,657
Maybe.

569
00:22:06,658 --> 00:22:07,783
His corpse will be inside.

570
00:22:07,784 --> 00:22:09,201
What will we do with him?

571
00:22:09,202 --> 00:22:10,912
- He's missing.
- Yes.

572
00:22:12,539 --> 00:22:13,664
THE SCAREDY-CAT SIBLINGS BREAK DOWN

573
00:22:13,665 --> 00:22:15,333
- Ahn Mu-seong must be dead.
- We need to check.

574
00:22:15,334 --> 00:22:16,667
He's probably dead.

575
00:22:16,668 --> 00:22:19,211
- But we saw a ghost on the livestream.
- I'm so scared.

576
00:22:19,212 --> 00:22:23,758
TOO SCARED TO TAKE A STEP

577
00:22:23,759 --> 00:22:25,427
We could die, but that's fine.
Let's go in.

578
00:22:27,763 --> 00:22:28,889
I mean…

579
00:22:29,473 --> 00:22:31,641
I really hate female ghosts.

580
00:22:33,310 --> 00:22:34,644
CAUTIOUS

581
00:22:35,270 --> 00:22:36,187
What?

582
00:22:36,188 --> 00:22:37,646
CLUNK

583
00:22:37,647 --> 00:22:39,024
Can we go?

584
00:22:41,777 --> 00:22:42,861
Yong-jin.

585
00:22:54,706 --> 00:22:56,416
- You're being brave today.
- He really is.

586
00:22:56,917 --> 00:22:57,959
You're usually a coward.

587
00:22:59,503 --> 00:23:01,046
- That was always closed.
- It's just this side.

588
00:23:01,922 --> 00:23:03,047
John?

589
00:23:03,048 --> 00:23:04,758
JOHN TAKES A LOOK

590
00:23:09,846 --> 00:23:11,263
- Oh, damn it.
- Why?

591
00:23:11,264 --> 00:23:12,264
Do you see him?

592
00:23:12,265 --> 00:23:13,808
- Is it him?
- What is it?

593
00:23:13,809 --> 00:23:14,850
What's going on?

594
00:23:14,851 --> 00:23:16,603
- He's sitting.
- Who is?

595
00:23:21,817 --> 00:23:22,859
Is it the ghost?

596
00:23:24,528 --> 00:23:25,695
It's Ahn Mu-seong.

597
00:23:27,197 --> 00:23:28,364
He's really sitting there.

598
00:23:28,365 --> 00:23:29,323
Can I take a look?

599
00:23:29,324 --> 00:23:30,867
Ahn Mu-seong is sitting inside?

600
00:23:31,451 --> 00:23:34,537
He's crouching on the floor like this.

601
00:23:34,538 --> 00:23:36,789
I can see him.

602
00:23:36,790 --> 00:23:38,916
Let's go in.

603
00:23:38,917 --> 00:23:40,293
Wait.

604
00:23:41,336 --> 00:23:42,212
What do we do?

605
00:23:54,641 --> 00:23:56,100
We're really going inside?

606
00:23:56,101 --> 00:23:57,602
- I'm scared.
- Gabee, go on.

607
00:24:01,356 --> 00:24:03,357
- I can't do this.
- Wasn't there a switch?

608
00:24:03,358 --> 00:24:04,650
Karina, can you do this?

609
00:24:04,651 --> 00:24:05,777
I don't think so.

610
00:24:08,655 --> 00:24:11,198
NEXT TO AHN MU-SEONG ON THE FLOOR

611
00:24:11,199 --> 00:24:13,201
THERE IS A PHONE

612
00:24:22,335 --> 00:24:23,503
Wait, first…

613
00:24:24,045 --> 00:24:25,671
I think we need this.

614
00:24:25,672 --> 00:24:27,464
Hye-ri, you're so brave.

615
00:24:27,465 --> 00:24:29,633
There's a rope.

616
00:24:29,634 --> 00:24:30,594
Oh, I got it.

617
00:24:35,182 --> 00:24:36,682
- There we go.
- That'll do.

618
00:24:36,683 --> 00:24:41,812
CRYPT

619
00:24:41,813 --> 00:24:43,397
THE ROPE WHERE THE VESSEL WAS HANGING

620
00:24:43,398 --> 00:24:47,401
TRACES OF SHAMANIC RITUALS

621
00:24:47,402 --> 00:24:49,695
- Hye-ri is so brave.
- Let's go in.

622
00:24:49,696 --> 00:24:51,280
I'm so proud of her.

623
00:24:51,281 --> 00:24:53,658
HYE-RI IS ESPECIALLY BRAVE TODAY

624
00:24:54,868 --> 00:24:57,162
I think he's dead.

625
00:24:59,748 --> 00:25:02,292
A paper talisman was inside.

626
00:25:03,210 --> 00:25:04,710
It's a paper talisman.

627
00:25:04,711 --> 00:25:06,254
A PAPER TALISMAN WRAPPED
AROUND A WOODEN BOX

628
00:25:06,838 --> 00:25:08,673
- It's a paper talisman.
- Yes.

629
00:25:11,259 --> 00:25:13,094
- He died like this.
- On the spot?

630
00:25:18,767 --> 00:25:20,310
I found another light.

631
00:25:21,394 --> 00:25:22,978
HEADS SWIVELING

632
00:25:22,979 --> 00:25:24,688
I keep looking back because I'm so scared.

633
00:25:24,689 --> 00:25:25,649
Same.

634
00:25:27,317 --> 00:25:30,319
- This is that human…
- It's the hand.

635
00:25:30,320 --> 00:25:31,612
IT'S THE HAND FROM THE VIDEO

636
00:25:31,613 --> 00:25:32,781
<i>Isn't that a human hand?</i>

637
00:25:35,033 --> 00:25:37,201
Do we need to take this paper talisman?

638
00:25:37,202 --> 00:25:38,494
- Should we?
- Let's take it.

639
00:25:38,495 --> 00:25:39,954
- I think we should.
- Yes.

640
00:25:39,955 --> 00:25:40,871
Take the hand too.

641
00:25:40,872 --> 00:25:42,122
- Take the hand?
- The hand?

642
00:25:42,123 --> 00:25:45,210
We should put it back where it belongs.

643
00:25:46,002 --> 00:25:48,295
Wait, something is falling.

644
00:25:48,296 --> 00:25:52,258
WATER IS DRIPPING FROM THE CEILING

645
00:25:52,259 --> 00:25:53,926
- It's water.
- It's dripping.

646
00:25:53,927 --> 00:25:55,010
STARTLED

647
00:25:55,011 --> 00:25:56,595
It's black water!

648
00:25:56,596 --> 00:25:57,805
- It's black water.
- It's black.

649
00:25:57,806 --> 00:25:59,432
- Let's get out.
- We need to go.

650
00:26:00,141 --> 00:26:01,850
The black water is dripping.

651
00:26:01,851 --> 00:26:03,227
STARTING TO COME DOWN MORE HEAVILY

652
00:26:03,228 --> 00:26:04,603
- Let's go.
- John, get the…

653
00:26:04,604 --> 00:26:05,854
- Get the paper talisman.
- Let's go.

654
00:26:05,855 --> 00:26:07,064
- Let's go.
- Yes.

655
00:26:07,065 --> 00:26:08,608
STEP OUT FOR NOW

656
00:26:09,234 --> 00:26:11,652
Okay, nobody better come out!

657
00:26:11,653 --> 00:26:13,362
I'm really scared.

658
00:26:13,363 --> 00:26:15,739
- I'll hit you!
- I really will attack.

659
00:26:15,740 --> 00:26:17,950
- I will hit you. Stay away.
- I do Taekwondo.

660
00:26:17,951 --> 00:26:19,910
I will hit you even if you're a ghost.

661
00:26:19,911 --> 00:26:21,203
- Here I go.
- It was black water.

662
00:26:21,204 --> 00:26:22,121
What about the hand?

663
00:26:22,122 --> 00:26:25,833
The black liquid started
spilling out at I-jang's house.

664
00:26:25,834 --> 00:26:26,792
It did.

665
00:26:26,793 --> 00:26:28,419
What is it?

666
00:26:28,420 --> 00:26:30,004
The water…

667
00:26:30,005 --> 00:26:31,547
It's coming out from here too.

668
00:26:31,548 --> 00:26:32,715
It's here too?

669
00:26:32,716 --> 00:26:33,800
- Yes.
- It's everywhere.

670
00:26:38,263 --> 00:26:40,389
- I'm so scared.
- Is it coming after us?

671
00:26:40,390 --> 00:26:42,933
- It's spreading through the village.
- Yes.

672
00:26:42,934 --> 00:26:44,184
I'm terrified.

673
00:26:44,185 --> 00:26:45,519
Should we check the phone?

674
00:26:45,520 --> 00:26:47,146
- Yes, let's check it.
- Yes.

675
00:26:47,147 --> 00:26:48,063
Good idea.

676
00:26:48,064 --> 00:26:49,356
ZERO-FEAR MU-SEONG TV
ENTER YOUR UNLOCK PATTERN

677
00:26:49,357 --> 00:26:50,816
IT'S A LOCKED SCREEN

678
00:26:50,817 --> 00:26:52,192
- We need to unlock it.
- The pattern.

679
00:26:52,193 --> 00:26:53,819
His phone wasn't in the video.

680
00:26:53,820 --> 00:26:55,362
- We didn't see a pattern.
- No, we didn't.

681
00:26:55,363 --> 00:26:56,447
Do we need to go back?

682
00:26:56,448 --> 00:26:57,990
- Maybe it's Z.
- Zero-fear?

683
00:26:57,991 --> 00:26:59,075
Since it's Zero-fear.

684
00:26:59,659 --> 00:27:02,244
IS THE CHANNEL NAME THE ANSWER?

685
00:27:02,245 --> 00:27:03,829
ENTERING THE Z OF ZERO

686
00:27:03,830 --> 00:27:04,747
WRONG

687
00:27:04,748 --> 00:27:05,873
That's not it.

688
00:27:05,874 --> 00:27:07,041
Can we try another Z?

689
00:27:07,042 --> 00:27:08,083
Could it be a smaller Z?

690
00:27:08,084 --> 00:27:09,585
WRONG

691
00:27:09,586 --> 00:27:11,337
- Maybe it's Z, I.
- Try that.

692
00:27:11,338 --> 00:27:13,839
- You mean like this?
- Swipe up.

693
00:27:13,840 --> 00:27:14,840
That's not it.

694
00:27:14,841 --> 00:27:17,217
It can lock us out
if we fail too many times.

695
00:27:17,218 --> 00:27:18,553
- Sorry.
- It's okay.

696
00:27:19,262 --> 00:27:20,263
Wait.

697
00:27:21,139 --> 00:27:22,473
This can't be it, right?

698
00:27:22,474 --> 00:27:23,891
I think the hand was in there.

699
00:27:23,892 --> 00:27:25,267
- It was.
- Yes.

700
00:27:25,268 --> 00:27:26,811
This isn't it, is it?

701
00:27:27,437 --> 00:27:28,771
Should we try M?

702
00:27:28,772 --> 00:27:29,939
It could be M for MS.

703
00:27:30,523 --> 00:27:31,607
Try a big M.

704
00:27:31,608 --> 00:27:33,192
IS IT THE M OF MS?

705
00:27:33,193 --> 00:27:34,401
WRONG

706
00:27:34,402 --> 00:27:36,278
- I thought it could be "NO."
- No?

707
00:27:36,279 --> 00:27:38,364
- Since he kept saying…
- You mean N?

708
00:27:38,365 --> 00:27:41,367
Ahn Mu-seong kept making this gesture.

709
00:27:41,368 --> 00:27:42,576
- Wasn't it an X?
- It's an X.

710
00:27:42,577 --> 00:27:43,827
- I see.
- It's his catchphrase.

711
00:27:43,828 --> 00:27:45,162
Because it means "no"?

712
00:27:45,163 --> 00:27:46,747
The gesture he kept making?

713
00:27:46,748 --> 00:27:50,125
AHN MU-SEONG'S SIGNATURE GESTURE, X

714
00:27:50,126 --> 00:27:51,293
- That could be it.
- Yes.

715
00:27:51,294 --> 00:27:53,045
That could be the unlock pattern.

716
00:27:53,046 --> 00:27:54,338
- So, what do we do?
- Try this.

717
00:27:54,339 --> 00:27:55,964
- Do it like this.
- Start with three.

718
00:27:55,965 --> 00:27:57,674
- Try 3, 5, 7.
- Okay.

719
00:27:57,675 --> 00:27:59,760
- Then 4, 1, and go down.
- Yes.

720
00:27:59,761 --> 00:28:01,595
- It starts with three, right?
- Yes.

721
00:28:01,596 --> 00:28:03,889
- His gesture.
- It's this, right?

722
00:28:03,890 --> 00:28:04,807
UNLOCKED

723
00:28:04,808 --> 00:28:06,350
- We did it.
- It worked?

724
00:28:06,351 --> 00:28:07,393
Unbelievable.

725
00:28:07,394 --> 00:28:10,396
- It was a meaningful gesture.
- It was.

726
00:28:10,397 --> 00:28:11,940
- Open KakaoTalk.
- Go to his messages.

727
00:28:12,524 --> 00:28:15,734
- Look at those messages.
- Why are there so many?

728
00:28:15,735 --> 00:28:17,486
THE POPULAR YOUTUBER
HAS A FLOOD OF MESSAGES

729
00:28:17,487 --> 00:28:20,740
- It's because he went missing.
- Right.

730
00:28:21,282 --> 00:28:23,867
- Most are video requests.
- They're all requests.

731
00:28:23,868 --> 00:28:26,286
- It says, "Why aren't you replying?"
- It's Deok-u.

732
00:28:26,287 --> 00:28:27,371
AN UNREAD MESSAGE FROM DEOK-U

733
00:28:27,372 --> 00:28:28,872
- There's a note.
- A note?

734
00:28:28,873 --> 00:28:30,290
There's a note?

735
00:28:30,291 --> 00:28:31,834
FOUND A NOTE

736
00:28:31,835 --> 00:28:34,336
"A woman walks around the reservoir."

737
00:28:34,337 --> 00:28:37,506
"She seems like
the shaman Deok-u described."

738
00:28:37,507 --> 00:28:39,842
"She went into Yonghandang Shrine."

739
00:28:39,843 --> 00:28:41,343
- "It's her home."
- "Stays in after 8 p.m."

740
00:28:41,344 --> 00:28:43,011
She must be home now.

741
00:28:43,012 --> 00:28:45,098
- What about photos?
- Yes, let's look.

742
00:28:45,682 --> 00:28:48,016
- What? It's a middle-aged lady.
- She went in.

743
00:28:48,017 --> 00:28:49,644
- She must be the shaman.
- It's her?

744
00:28:50,311 --> 00:28:54,022
CASUALLY ENTERING THE CRYPT

745
00:28:54,023 --> 00:28:58,360
- I think she held rituals until recently.
- I guess so.

746
00:28:58,361 --> 00:28:59,862
She came back out and…

747
00:28:59,863 --> 00:29:01,989
SHE WALKED UP A MOUNTAIN

748
00:29:01,990 --> 00:29:03,907
She went up that way.

749
00:29:03,908 --> 00:29:05,577
- She took that path.
- Yes.

750
00:29:06,703 --> 00:29:08,036
- She went up to the temple.
- Right.

751
00:29:08,037 --> 00:29:08,996
- Yeah.
- Is that it?

752
00:29:08,997 --> 00:29:11,248
- We need to go there.
- We have to go to the temple.

753
00:29:11,249 --> 00:29:12,249
She knows everything.

754
00:29:12,250 --> 00:29:13,375
I think she's Shin Nae-ryeong.

755
00:29:13,376 --> 00:29:15,127
- I think so.
- Those are the only photos.

756
00:29:15,128 --> 00:29:20,466
It seemed Shin Nae-ryeong
was taking care of the vessel.

757
00:29:20,467 --> 00:29:22,426
In order to meet her,

758
00:29:22,427 --> 00:29:24,928
<i>we had to go to Yonghandang Shrine.</i>

759
00:29:24,929 --> 00:29:26,263
We have to go.

760
00:29:26,264 --> 00:29:28,265
- Yonghandang Shrine.
- Yes.

761
00:29:28,266 --> 00:29:29,642
I think I'll have nightmares today.

762
00:29:31,394 --> 00:29:33,937
Do-hoon, let's do a video call.

763
00:29:33,938 --> 00:29:36,023
- You'll wait until I fall asleep?
- Of course.

764
00:29:36,024 --> 00:29:37,941
Hye-ri, can I sleep over at your place?

765
00:29:37,942 --> 00:29:39,067
Yes, if you have nightmares…

766
00:29:39,068 --> 00:29:41,236
- Should we have a sleepover?
- Good idea.

767
00:29:41,237 --> 00:29:42,154
Come to my house.

768
00:29:42,155 --> 00:29:45,282
- Since it's the final day…
- Let's all sleep at Hye-ri's house.

769
00:29:45,283 --> 00:29:46,493
Good idea.

770
00:29:47,202 --> 00:29:48,452
I'm so scared.

771
00:29:48,453 --> 00:29:50,329
I feel like someone is behind us.

772
00:29:50,330 --> 00:29:52,081
My zodiac said
I should laugh if I get scared.

773
00:29:52,582 --> 00:29:53,749
LAUGHING

774
00:29:53,750 --> 00:29:54,917
Let's go.

775
00:29:54,918 --> 00:29:56,210
CURRENT LOCATION

776
00:29:56,211 --> 00:29:58,378
- I will actually hit them.
- It's here.

777
00:29:58,379 --> 00:30:00,547
I will lash out!

778
00:30:00,548 --> 00:30:02,549
Doesn't it help to have weapons?

779
00:30:02,550 --> 00:30:03,967
- It does.
- But I'm so scared.

780
00:30:03,968 --> 00:30:07,012
- Me too.
- There really is no one around.

781
00:30:07,013 --> 00:30:09,306
- They all ran away.
- Yes.

782
00:30:09,307 --> 00:30:11,266
- I would have left too.
- Me too.

783
00:30:11,267 --> 00:30:12,851
I'd get out so fast if I weren't an agent.

784
00:30:12,852 --> 00:30:14,437
- I would have been the first to go.
- Same.

785
00:30:16,356 --> 00:30:17,397
- That's it.
- We're here.

786
00:30:17,398 --> 00:30:18,440
We're here.

787
00:30:18,441 --> 00:30:19,733
Oh, my.

788
00:30:19,734 --> 00:30:22,444
Why does this place exist?

789
00:30:22,445 --> 00:30:25,697
- Feels like something is bound to happen.
- Right?

790
00:30:25,698 --> 00:30:27,866
- This is the real deal.
- It's so suspicious.

791
00:30:27,867 --> 00:30:28,701
YONGHANDANG SHRINE

792
00:30:31,079 --> 00:30:32,955
A FRONT YARD WITH STRONG SHAMANIC VIBES

793
00:30:32,956 --> 00:30:35,375
It feels so eerie.

794
00:30:37,335 --> 00:30:38,461
If you ask me,

795
00:30:39,295 --> 00:30:41,171
this is the highlight.

796
00:30:41,172 --> 00:30:42,297
- It is.
- Right?

797
00:30:42,298 --> 00:30:46,343
But if we want to break the curse,

798
00:30:46,344 --> 00:30:47,970
- we have to go inside.
- That's true.

799
00:30:47,971 --> 00:30:49,721
But can the curse be broken?

800
00:30:49,722 --> 00:30:52,432
Can't we just ask Shin Nae-ryeong?

801
00:30:52,433 --> 00:30:53,934
Do you think she's inside?

802
00:30:53,935 --> 00:30:55,060
She must be home.

803
00:30:55,061 --> 00:30:57,729
- She must be.
- I hope she's safe and sound.

804
00:30:57,730 --> 00:30:58,731
This is Yonghandang Shrine.

805
00:30:59,274 --> 00:31:00,817
My name uses the same Chinese character.

806
00:31:01,317 --> 00:31:04,027
This is so crazy.

807
00:31:04,028 --> 00:31:05,112
USES THE SAME "YONG" CHINESE CHARACTER

808
00:31:05,113 --> 00:31:07,072
- Let's go in.
- My heart is racing so fast.

809
00:31:07,073 --> 00:31:08,073
It's pounding, right?

810
00:31:08,074 --> 00:31:11,452
SLOWLY APPROACHING YONGHANDANG SHRINE

811
00:31:13,830 --> 00:31:15,206
It opened.

812
00:31:17,584 --> 00:31:21,337
THE DOOR OPENED BY ITSELF

813
00:31:22,130 --> 00:31:23,755
Stop, you're kidding.

814
00:31:23,756 --> 00:31:25,507
Why would it open by itself?

815
00:31:25,508 --> 00:31:28,427
It opened as if it was expecting us.

816
00:31:28,428 --> 00:31:30,554
I didn't want to go in, but we had to.

817
00:31:30,555 --> 00:31:33,016
We had to look for clues.

818
00:31:33,975 --> 00:31:35,225
Let's go.

819
00:31:35,226 --> 00:31:38,061
- Did she know we were coming?
- We're being invited.

820
00:31:38,062 --> 00:31:40,022
- She knows everything.
- I'm scared.

821
00:31:40,023 --> 00:31:41,023
ENTERING CAUTIOUSLY

822
00:31:41,024 --> 00:31:43,901
- Okay.
- This place is safe, right?

823
00:31:43,902 --> 00:31:45,319
- You're right.
- Yes.

824
00:31:45,320 --> 00:31:47,572
<i>They won over all the opposing residents</i>

825
00:31:48,239 --> 00:31:51,116
<i>except for Shin Nae-ryeong.</i>

826
00:31:51,117 --> 00:31:53,911
Shin Nae-ryeong might
know what the black fluid is.

827
00:31:53,912 --> 00:31:56,079
THE PLACE TO MEET SHIN NAE-RYEONG
AND LEARN THE CURSE'S SECRET

828
00:31:56,080 --> 00:31:57,581
This place is okay.

829
00:31:57,582 --> 00:31:58,750
It's safe here.

830
00:31:59,542 --> 00:32:02,211
This is the safest place in the village.

831
00:32:03,796 --> 00:32:04,713
Is anyone here?

832
00:32:04,714 --> 00:32:06,841
IT'S PEACEFUL INSIDE YONGHANDANG SHRINE

833
00:32:07,800 --> 00:32:09,092
