855
00:33:04,983 --> 00:33:06,692
Hello, Ms. Shin.

856
00:33:06,693 --> 00:33:08,236
Who is it?

857
00:33:08,861 --> 00:33:10,363
Hello, Ms. Shin.

858
00:33:10,863 --> 00:33:12,240
Who are you?

859
00:33:12,824 --> 00:33:14,117
- We are…
- Hello.

860
00:33:15,076 --> 00:33:16,368
