- It wasn't us.

875
00:33:53,448 --> 00:33:54,740
We didn't do it.

876
00:33:54,741 --> 00:33:57,034
It was a YouTuber.

877
00:33:57,035 --> 00:33:58,453
His name is Ahn Mu-seong.

878
00:33:59,620 --> 00:34:01,913
- It was Ahn Mu-seong.
- What's the situation outside?

879
00:34:01,914 --> 00:34:04,082
There's no one around.

880
00:34:04,083 --> 00:34:07,044
There's black liquid everywhere.

881
00:34:07,045 --> 00:34:09,546
DID YOU SAY BLACK LIQUID?

882
00:34:09,547 --> 00:34:11,423
There are no people in the village.

883
00:34:11,424 --> 00:34:13,009
