- Bind yourself to this spell.

941
00:36:31,606 --> 00:36:33,982
- Sink beneath the ground.
- Sink beneath the ground.

942
00:36:33,983 --> 00:36:35,400
- Drift away with the stream.
- Drift away with the stream.

943
