- Okay.

955
00:36:58,132 --> 00:37:00,008
- Keep going without stopping!
- Yes, ma'am.

956
00:37:00,009 --> 00:37:03,178
- Earth below, breath above.
- Earth below, breath above.

957
00:37:03,179 --> 00:37:05,305
