- Drift away with the stream.

960
00:37:09,477 --> 00:37:12,812
- Earth below, breath above.
- Earth below, breath above.

961
00:37:12,813 --> 00:37:15,023
- Bind yourself to this spell.
- Bind yourself to this spell.

962
00:37:15,024 --> 00:37:16,441
- Sink beneath the ground.
- Sink beneath the ground.

963
00:37:16,442 --> 00:37:18,568
- Drift away with the stream.
- Drift away with the stream.

964
00:37:18,569 --> 00:37:21,655
- Earth below, breath above.
- Earth below, breath above.

965
00:37:21,656 --> 00:37:23,782
- Bind yourself to this spell.
- Bind yourself to this spell.

966
00:37:23,783 --> 00:37:26,994
PRAYING DILIGENTLY

967
00:37:27,662 --> 00:37:31,164
SHIN NAE-RYEONG OPENS
THE LOCKED DOOR AND LEAVES

968
00:37:31,165 --> 00:37:34,668
- Earth below, breath above.
- Earth below, breath above.

969
00:37:34,669 --> 00:37:36,962
- Bind yourself to this spell.
- Bind yourself to this spell.

970
00:37:36,963 --> 00:37:40,882
- Earth below, breath above.
- Earth below, breath above.

971
00:37:40,883 --> 00:37:42,926
- Bind yourself to this spell.
- Bind yourself to this spell.

