- Can we?
- Do we have to keep chanting?

1004
00:39:00,087 --> 00:39:01,546
It feels safer.

1005
00:39:01,547 --> 00:39:02,964
Let's mumble it to be safe.

1006
00:39:02,965 --> 00:39:04,799
ALL THEY CAN TRUST NOW IS PRAYER

1007
00:39:04,800 --> 00:39:06,343
The door is open!

1008
00:39:06,344 --> 00:39:08,178
- The door is open.
- Yes.

1009
00:39:08,179 --> 00:39:10,014
- Was it closed earlier?
- Yes, it was.

1010
00:39:12,391 --> 00:39:13,516
You're right. It's open.

1011
00:39:13,517 --> 00:39:14,434
FOUND THE DOOR OPEN

1012
00:39:14,435 --> 00:39:15,852
Oh, you mean that door.

1013
00:39:15,853 --> 00:39:17,312
WALKING TOWARD THE OPEN DOOR

1014
00:39:17,313 --> 00:39:18,563
- Earth below.
- Earth below.

1015
00:39:18,564 --> 00:39:20,315
START THE PRAYER NATURALLY

1016
00:39:20,316 --> 00:39:22,818
- I think we can stop now.
- Bind yourself to this spell.

1017
00:39:23,319 --> 00:39:25,446
But that shaman lady…

1018
00:39:26,530 --> 00:39:28,114
She's dead, right?

1019
00:39:28,115 --> 00:39:29,032
Sink beneath the ground.

1020
00:39:29,033 --> 00:39:30,325
But does that mean

1021
00:39:30,326 --> 00:39:32,619
- our chanting didn't work?
- Drift away with the stream.

1022
00:39:32,620 --> 00:39:34,579
- Earth below.
- Maybe it protected us.

1023
00:39:34,580 --> 00:39:36,831
Maybe that's why we're okay.

1024
00:39:36,832 --> 00:39:37,792
A NEW SPACE BEYOND THE DOOR

1025
00:39:43,506 --> 00:39:46,049
A NARROW CORRIDOR WITH RED LIGHTS

1026
00:39:46,050 --> 00:39:48,343
It was a red corridor.

1027
00:39:48,344 --> 00:39:51,513
We saw a new pattern on the walls.

1028
00:39:51,514 --> 00:39:54,475
It was very chilling and unpleasant.

1029
00:39:55,351 --> 00:39:57,353
It smells a bit…

1030
00:39:58,604 --> 00:39:59,896
- Breath above.
- Breath above.

1031
00:39:59,897 --> 00:40:01,648
- Bind yourself to this spell.
- Bind yourself to this spell.

1032
00:40:01,649 --> 00:40:04,275
Sink beneath the ground,
drift away with the stream.

1033
00:40:04,276 --> 00:40:05,443
MOVING FORWARD SLOWLY WHILE CHANTING

1034
00:40:05,444 --> 00:40:08,447
- Earth below, breath above.
- Earth below, breath above.

1035
00:40:17,081 --> 00:40:18,374
Oh, no!

1036
00:40:18,958 --> 00:40:20,960
FOUND SHIN NAE-RYEONG'S SHOES

1037
00:40:21,627 --> 00:40:22,586
What is it?

1038
00:41:54,470 --> 00:41:59,475
Subtitle translation by: Hannah Og Nam
